{"tid":1962013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【城市傷痕】港漂出書談「修例風波」","createTime":"2020-04-07T07:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T11:46:58.000Z","uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"16e189cd03d8d810f50cc9a921b9d99432d4b816","tid":1962013,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/26/29/10262964_953689.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F26%2F29%2F10262964_953689.jpg&h=9139decf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《城市傷痕：港漂眼中的香港修例風波》<br />\n作者：一川<br />\n出版社：利文出版社<br />\n出版時間：2020年4月<br />\n<br />\n香港修例風波綿延至今，震盪、撕裂、衝突過後造成的傷痕，除了印刻在這座城市的每個角落，更是讓每位關心、愛護這座城市的人內心疼痛。<br />\n<br />\n城市的「傷痕」<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月1日，遊行結束後，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">部分「黑衣蒙面人」衝入立法會大樓，將內部破壞殆盡</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n傍晚時分，從會展中心沿着海濱走去中環，吹着海風，對面的尖沙咀文化中心的外牆，不知甚麼時候開始有了多媒體燈光秀，和ICC的動態卡通一高一低，相映成趣。"},{"pid":"064fb7953ee2e32fc299f35df782ab879d61a432","tid":1962013,"uid":124983,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"得啦 漂返大陸唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a4aefdabab6665cbb36ed0039d155fd8d1b53e","tid":1962013,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"這些僅僅是城市留下的「傷痕」，而我們的心呢？內心的「傷痕」又需要多少時間才能撫平？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/26/29/10262966_123363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F26%2F29%2F10262966_123363.jpg&h=a80f59a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新書《城市傷痕：港漂眼中的香港修例風波》，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">從一名資深「港漂」的特殊視角出發</span></strong>，結合其個人親歷事件所思所感及媒體新聞報道評論，寫下你、我、他在修例風波中的城市故事。<br />\n<br />\n多元社會思考<br />\n<br />\n全書收錄25個短篇，內文配以事件背景資料及作者親手繪製的漫畫，從購物經歷、家庭糾紛、出行故事，到連儂牆的本意、媒體報道的角度、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">粵方言傳承的觀點&hellip;&hellip;</span></strong>，以切身感受和朋友敘事為線索，試圖勾勒出這次風波對個人、家庭、外來移民、本地居民的影響，以及對媒體、教育、行政、社會撕裂、群組壓力、弱勢群體等的多元社會思考。"},{"pid":"439c561e4d9e8246dd7f4aac52e943ee4b09248e","tid":1962013,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:34:58.000Z","msg":"正如作者在後記中所言，在修例風波後香港人以至全球，共同面對的是新型冠狀病毒，冀望彼此能「攜手而行，重新拾起失落的勇氣，站回自己應屬的崗位，做到自己應盡的職責，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">秉持海納百川的氣度</span></strong>，方見得到城市更加美好的未來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/26/29/10262965_768389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F26%2F29%2F10262965_768389.jpg&h=60b29767&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bb76da70fe69d3e7d3acd4ced3bfef9edab9026","tid":1962013,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:37:05.000Z","msg":"香港抗爭者仲未有人出本書做紀錄真係失策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾共諜體系佔哂先機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（哩本同周顯嗰幾本）<br />\n<br />\n反而台灣有出一本"},{"pid":"6d5cca79e97b77c750c53f1fea84e27e3a4aed28","tid":1962013,"uid":53062,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:38:23.000Z","msg":"關你港漂撚事咩"},{"pid":"1f02b962fb4e926f4b659265bfcdeef253ba99f9","tid":1962013,"uid":185656,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲就蝗蟲啦,港漂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72da5613075fef273c77d8a9374e9558abe9293f","tid":1962013,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bb76da70fe69d3e7d3acd4ced3bfef9edab9026","tid":1962013,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:37:05.000Z","msg":"香港抗爭者仲未有人出本書做紀錄真係失策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾共諜體系佔哂先機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（哩本同周顯嗰幾本）<br />\n<br />\n反而台灣有出一本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"日本都有人出左本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4594084001/ref=cm_sw_r_cp_api_i_y5cJEbS3G3V1X\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2Fdp%2F4594084001%2Fref%3Dcm_sw_r_cp_api_i_y5cJEbS3G3V1X&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=b13f137c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4594084001/ref=cm_sw_r_cp_api_i_y5cJEbS3G3V1X</a>"},{"pid":"7eb1dff5d736f77164b83c27627d8274d82c314f","tid":1962013,"uid":156121,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"港漂呢個詞從來都係支那人用語<br />\n高級蝗蟲"},{"pid":"ed4933cf934c7223bb465888002e49309804d15b","tid":1962013,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d5cca79e97b77c750c53f1fea84e27e3a4aed28","tid":1962013,"uid":53062,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:38:23.000Z","msg":"關你港漂撚事咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:41:16.000Z","msg":"成班鵲巢鳩佔"},{"pid":"d046d32b801cedd6d4cf67ced679627201140e39","tid":1962013,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:42:14.000Z","msg":"立場係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544ab5411ea0e9bbfed05dc9a078a393e6db8af6","tid":1962013,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:42:50.000Z","msg":"在修例風波後?<br />\n佢覺得完左？陳同佳都未去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ca5b6fe25fb54b02ca8bfbdcaa89601c9bb20c","tid":1962013,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d046d32b801cedd6d4cf67ced679627201140e39","tid":1962013,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dis